      <title>伊拉克称上个月其石油产量低于 OPEC+ 的配额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/iraq-says-it-pumped-below-opec-oil-production-quota-last-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊拉克表示，为了更好地遵守 OPEC+ 平衡全球原油市场的努力，伊拉克上个月的石油产量低于其 OPEC+ 石油产量配额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-12/iraq-says-it-pumped-below-opec-oil-production-quota-last-month</guid>
